message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.LG, cs.CY. The paper describes a conversational agent that assists NLP researchers in finding and exploring scientific literature, identifying relevant authors, planning or post-processing conference visits, and preparing paper submissions. This falls under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), machine learning (cs.LG), and cybernetics (cs.CY).
